title: Proposal to Mint a WHOAMI identity on t3rm.dev
body:
YeetDAO can collect NFTs from the most innovative projects on Ethereum. Let's start with a T3RM.dev WHOAMI identity NFT.

This is a proposal to transfer enough Eth from the DAO to cover the cost of 1 new WHOAMI NFT minting from t3rm.dev.
author: 0x5F81A789DFa30AA811Be4D4649e513ab027028d2
